text:
Kaho's highlighter pen is so cute~!
Look, Rinze-chan! It's a Shiba Inu print...!

Come to think of it, when I was a student
There were people who had all sorts of stationery.

!!
Did everyone have Shiba Inu pens?!

Was it
A glittery pen, maybe?

I saw scented
Erasers, for sure.

We did
Swap stickers, I think...

Oh yeah~! They had them, right?
They even had fruit-scented ones, and chocolate ones too──

The stickers were...
Supplied by Kaho-san...

Yes,
I have a lot of them~!
